channel.title: Zaros-rsps Pking based 2015
channel.description:
[CENTER][SIZE=6]About zaros?[/SIZE] Zaros is a pking based private server, and its still in beta. Joey the owner tries to make this server a little different. We have a cool donate system that gives you a mystery box with a rare. Voting system will be added soon, you're reward will be 5 pk points each page.
[SIZE=6]Features[/SIZE] - Bosses - Flawless switching - Clan chat - Great combat system - Titles (pking) - Pking store. - Spawntab - Spawncommands - ::master / ::pure
This is zaros rsps, zaros is not playable yet, i am looking for a vps that i can pay with paysafecard. if anyone knows one please hook me up!
